 the&nbsp;<em>point of focus.&nbsp;</em>The imaginary two dimensional plane=
 that extends from that point is known as the&nbsp;<em>plane of focus</em>.=
</p><p>Any part of your image that falls directly on this plane is official=
ly <em>in focus.</em></p></div><div class=3D"thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element=
